## Links

A button can become a link if you add `href`.

<ComponentContainer>
	<Button on:click={() => alert('button')}>Button</Button>
	<Button href="#buttons">Link</Button>
</ComponentContainer>

```svelte
<Button on:click={() => alert('button')}>Button</Button>
<Button href="#buttons">Link</Button>
```

