## Squares

Adding `-square` to the end of a `size` will make it square.

<ComponentContainer>
	<Button size="square-xl">xl</Button>
	<Button size="square-lg">lg</Button>
	<Button size="square-md">md</Button>
	<Button size="square-sm">sm</Button>
</ComponentContainer>

```svelte
<Button size="square-xl">xl</Button>
<Button size="square-lg">lg</Button>
<Button size="square-md">md</Button>
<Button size="square-sm">sm</Button>
```

