## Prefix/Suffix

There is a `slot` for suffixes/prefixes.

<ComponentContainer>
	<Button>
		<span slot="prefix">�</span>
		Prefix
	</Button>
	<Button>
		<span slot="suffix">�</span>
		Suffix
	</Button>
</ComponentContainer>

```svelte
<Button>
	<span slot="prefix">�</span>
	Prefix
</Button>
<Button>
	<span slot="suffix">�</span>
	Suffix
</Button>
```
